fabric.messages

Enum Message.MessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Message.MessageType>
      • fabric.messages.Message.MessageType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Message.MessageType>
    Enclosing class:
    Message<R extends Message.Response,E extends FabricException>

    protected static enum Message.MessageType
extends java.lang.Enum<Message.MessageType>
    This enum gives a mapping between message types and ordinals. This is used for efficient encoding and decoding of the type of a message.
